name: Housing SnCT
description: A code from the SNOMED Clinical Terminology UK coding system which represent aspects of housing including current housing situation and suitability of housing. Any code from the SNOMED CT UK 'Housing' subset with subset original id 5991000000137; the corresponding SNOMED CT UK Refset fully specified name is 'Housing finding simple reference set (foundation metadata concept)' with Refset Id 999001541000000103.
